column1: 123-cardDelay-English~You can track the location of the card using this link: http://postprovider.com/track/12345

column2: there are technical issues with the mobile operator. Please try again later!

column1: atm-issue-English~This ATM is currently out of service. You can use the nearest ATM
123-cardDelay-Albanian~Vendndodhjen e karteles mund ta gjurmoni permes ketij linku http://postprovider.com/track/12345
123-mobile-sms-Albanian~Per momentin jepi duke pasur teknike me operatorin e vales. Ju lutemi provoni me vone!
atm-issue-Albanian~Ky atm per momentin eshte jasht funksionit. Ju mundeni ta perdorni atm-in me te afert qe eshte ne kete lokacion https://maps.app.goo.gl/CFdsaB1jyeKEYU54A
None-Albanian~Per momentin nuk mund te pergjigjem per kete pytje
